### 1️⃣ Create & Lock Escrow
POST http://localhost:3000/api/escrows
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "escrow_ref": "ESCROW12345",
  "order_id": "835c5e25-9ed7-4625-9f4d-387a20a04524",
  "amount": 500.00
}

###

### 2️⃣ Release Escrow
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/escrows/bfc0f1a1-5678-43a9-9d22-59b1fa123456/release
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "chain_tx": "0xblockchainReleaseTxHash"
}

###

### 3️⃣ Refund Escrow
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/escrows/bfc0f1a1-5678-43a9-9d22-59b1fa123456/refund
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "chain_tx": "0xblockchainRefundTxHash",
  "reason": "Order cancelled by buyer"
}

###

### 4️⃣ Upload Blockchain Proof
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/escrows/bfc0f1a1-5678-43a9-9d22-59b1fa123456/proof
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "chain_tx": "0xproofTxHash"
}

###

### 5️⃣ Get Escrow by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/escrows/bfc0f1a1-5678-43a9-9d22-59b1fa123456

###

### 6️⃣ List Escrows (filters)
# Locked escrows
GET http://localhost:3000/api/escrows?status=locked

###
# Released escrows for a specific order
GET http://localhost:3000/api/escrows?status=released&order_id=11111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111

###
# Search by escrow_ref
GET http://localhost:3000/api/escrows?escrow_ref=ESCROW12345
